Package org.jboss.windup.graph.model

Interface OrganizationModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.syncleus.ferma.ElementFrame, com.syncleus.ferma.VertexFrame, WindupFrame<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex>, WindupVertexFrame
    public interface OrganizationModel
extends WindupVertexFrame
    This classifies files and provides general background information about a specific ArchiveModel. (For instance, an XML file may be classified as a "XYZ Configuration File".) A OrganizationModel may also contain links to additional information, or auto-translated/generated/updated versions of the source file.
